title: 02/16/2021 – Hour 3 – JJ Watt Thinks Cleveland Rocks
itunes:title: 02/16/2021 – Hour 3 – JJ Watt Thinks Cleveland Rocks
description:
Rob and TJ react to the news that JJ Watt may be interested in joining the Cleveland Browns, and take some of your calls! Former NFL head coach Hue Jackson joins the show to talk about all the latest news coming out of the league, and Rob can’t believe that anyone would want to expand the College Football playoffs!
